overview: Future employees of Club Océan are obliged to go through the seminar box in order to train before taking up their duties in their respective clubs this summer! But instead of giving their all in order to improve, the novices spend their time teasing and flirting with each other... So much so that the last evening of the seminar is hotter than expected! Disguises, role-playing games, challenges, fortunately the surveillance video images remind them of their delicious nighttime adventures...
title: The Seminar
